r Gründerkrise die Schwächen des Normativsystems der Novelle von 1870 erkennen. Die neue Quellenedition stellt eine notwendige Ergänzung der Materialiensammlung zur Aktienrechtsreform von 1884 von Schubert und Hommelhoff von 1985 dar.   aThe Company Law Amendment of 11 June 1870 eliminated the requirement for a state license in accordance with the ADHGB of 1861 for the formation and administration of stock corporations, replacing it with a normative system. This publication contains a comprehensive and previously unpublished range of sources on the Federal Council of the North German Confederation’s deliberations on the amendment as well as early accounts of it in practice.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Aug 2020) 0aCorporation lawzGermanyxHistory. 0aStock companieszGermanyxHistory. 4aAktienrechtsnovelle 1870. 4aGerman Company Law Amendment of 1870. 7aLAW / Corporate.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2017z9783110547771oZDB-23-DGC0 cEPUBz97831105385400 cprintz978311053624940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311053875540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110538755423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110538755.jpg  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGCb2017  aZDB-23-DGGb2017